WEBVTT


00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:04.720
when people ask me to hang out over the weekend

00:00:04.721 --> 00:00:08.261
in theory I have nothing going on

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:10.220
but then I think to myself

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:16.340
how will I be able to do my daily minimum seven hours of doing nothing

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:21.040
being a sloth both Saturday and Sunday are very important to me

00:00:21.041 --> 00:00:25.221
I also have to hang out with my cats and eat my grilled dinners

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:29.374
so no I don't really have time for you, I'm sorry
